{title: Chord Font Directives}

{chordfont: Helvetica Bold}
{chordsize: 11}
{chordcolour: darkblue}

{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[Am]Chords in Helvetica [Em]Bold
[F]Dark blue and [G]eleven point
[Am]Standing out a[Em]bove the text
[F]At every [G]chord point
{end_of_verse}

{chordfont: Arial}
{chordsize: 14}
{chordcolour: #FF0000}

{start_of_chorus}
[C]Now chords in [G]Arial
[Am]Fourteen point [F]red
[C]Big and [G]bright
[Am]Overhead [F]spread
{end_of_chorus}
